  "elapsed_s": 116.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I really didn't know how the, the violin come between my hands.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But here was something that was decide-- decides eventually for the destiny of my life later on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was, in the beginning as a very little child, singing some of these melodies or trying to reproduce them in the xylophone.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because the violin was not producing sounds, this toy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Was attractive only with the-- perhaps with the [INAUDIBLE] the fact that eventually, the-- something like that in the future is possible to produce sounds.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from this early moments of my life, I started to show some preferences toward music.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was singing obviously in tune enough to carry a song from beginning until the end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this perhaps helped that when I reached the age almost of entering in a preschool class, preschool group, I, I was already able to, to sing a number of songs in, in a way in which they were able-- my, my parents were able to prove that their little child have a musical ear, which made them very happy at that time.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tell me about your parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a teacher in his early ages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Israel Polidi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was born in Ruse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was one of the oldest cities in Bulgaria and the time was kind of a spiritual center for Bulgaria.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was located on, on the river, Danube.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the reason why I was serving-- was so highly developed culturally was because was kind of connection between the culture of two countries, Bulgaria and Romania.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Matter of fact, the city was closer to Bucharest, which was the capital of Romania than to Sofia.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
